hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I didn't go to university ourmeds.org complaints Your point that "She displays this not by needing to prove to you that she's the smartest person in the room, but instead by always asking the right questions. If someone disagrees with her, her first instinct is not to try to bully them, but instead to try to understand why they have reached a different conclusion than she has." serves to contrast her style with the other often-mentioned candidate that you have not named. I prefer that style myself.
